13
00:03:09,970 --> 00:03:10,850
Symptoms?

14
00:03:11,490 --> 00:03:12,810
It's like,

15
00:03:14,650 --> 00:03:15,850
when I first saw you,

16
00:03:16,050 --> 00:03:16,890
the second time,

17
