27
00:03:38,970 --> 00:03:39,450
Oh right,

28
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:40,810
I forgot to ask last time.

29
00:03:41,130 --> 00:03:42,930
Why are you covered in scars?

30
00:03:45,530 --> 00:03:46,250
None of your concern.

31
00:03:47,329 --> 00:03:48,570
Perfect your makeup.

32
00:03:48,930 --> 00:03:49,730
Don't embarrass yourself again.

33
00:03:52,250 --> 00:03:53,650
What's your name then?

34
00:03:54,170 --> 00:03:55,530
We've known each other so long,

35
00:03:55,770 --> 00:03:57,050
