36
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:01,130
Jinxiu.

37
00:04:02,130 --> 00:04:03,050
Jinxiu?

38
00:04:05,330 --> 00:04:07,530
How can I reach you

39
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:09,010
when I need to?

40
00:04:10,850 --> 00:04:11,890
What's this about?

41
00:04:12,730 --> 00:04:14,290
I keep messing up here,

42
00:04:14,490 --> 00:04:15,570
and you know the ropes.

43
00:04:15,810 --> 00:04:16,850
Of course I'd need you.

44
00:04:18,370 --> 00:04:19,570
You're incorrigible.

45
00:04:26,530 --> 00:04:27,610
This is Lilybell.

46
00:04:28,970 --> 00:04:29,770
Speak to it.

47
00:04:32,130 --> 00:04:32,930
Jinxiu.

48
00:04:33,530 --> 00:04:34,210
[Jinxiu.]

49
00:04:35,290 --> 00:04:36,210
That's amazing!

50
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:38,930
Now you can use it to find me.

51
00:04:41,130 --> 00:04:41,850
Jinxiu.

52
00:04:42,370 --> 00:04:42,930
[Jinxiu.]

53
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:44,490
Jinxiu?

54
00:04:44,610 --> 00:04:45,130
[Jinxiu?]

55
00:04:45,290 --> 00:04:45,530
Enough.

56
00:04:45,690 --> 00:04:46,490
Jinxiu.

57
00:04:46,810 --> 00:04:47,250
Jin...

58
00:04:52,810 --> 00:04:53,490
Jinxiu.

59
00:05:15,530 --> 00:05:17,090
[I warned you before.]

60
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:19,810
[Only by divesting all emotion]

61
00:05:20,770 --> 00:05:21,930
[can you attain true impartiality.]

62
00:05:22,970 --> 00:05:24,570
[If your heart clings to anything,]

63
00:05:25,770 --> 00:05:28,690
[you'll never be a worthy punisher.]

64
00:05:40,330 --> 00:05:41,530
Still your heart,

65
00:05:42,130 --> 00:05:43,409
curb your desires.

66
00:05:43,690 --> 00:05:44,730
Still your heart,

67
00:05:45,570 --> 00:05:46,890
curb your desires.

68
00:05:48,050 --> 00:05:49,290
Still your heart,

69
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:51,370
curb your desires.

70
00:06:00,810 --> 00:06:03,370
Hongning! Where are you?

71
00:06:03,730 --> 00:06:04,850
I've said it a hundred times.

72
00:06:05,010 --> 00:06:06,650
The Floral Deity took her away.

73
00:06:06,970 --> 00:06:07,890
The tree, bird, and rabbit

74
00:06:07,970 --> 00:06:08,530
all witnessed it!

75
00:06:08,690 --> 00:06:09,770
Why won't you believe me?

76
00:06:10,610 --> 00:06:11,650
I just don't!

77
00:06:11,850 --> 00:06:13,370
[Hongning!]

78
00:06:16,730 --> 00:06:17,970
You're not my friend anymore.

79
00:06:19,810 --> 00:06:20,530
Seriously?

80
00:06:21,090 --> 00:06:22,370
If she's locked up

81
00:06:22,810 --> 00:06:24,130
over some tiny slip-up,

82
00:06:24,610 --> 00:06:25,370
you and I would've been in jail

83
00:06:25,970 --> 00:06:27,210
like a million times by now.

84
00:06:27,410 --> 00:06:28,330
C'mon!

85
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:29,930
We just pull harmless pranks,

86
00:06:30,450 --> 00:06:31,330
gossip about deities.

87
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:32,610
Hongning's different!

88
00:06:32,930 --> 00:06:34,450
She broke the Floral Oath!

89
00:06:36,210 --> 00:06:36,930
It's like you slapped

90
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:38,770
the Floral Deity right in the face!

91
00:06:38,890 --> 00:06:39,850
That'd piss him off.

92
00:06:41,450 --> 00:06:43,130
Let alone he's a punisher!

93
00:06:43,250 --> 00:06:43,810
Oh no.

94
00:06:44,290 --> 00:06:46,210
Hongning's gonna be skinned alive!

95
00:06:46,570 --> 00:06:47,530
Don't jinx her!

96
00:06:49,970 --> 00:06:50,650
I won't believe it.

97
00:06:51,170 --> 00:06:52,250
Stop talking nonsense!

98
00:06:52,770 --> 00:06:54,170
I won't believe she's gone!

99
00:06:55,810 --> 00:06:56,810
Ningmeng.

100
00:06:57,330 --> 00:06:59,330
I beg you.

101
00:07:00,050 --> 00:07:02,050
Send someone

102
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:03,170
to ask around.

103
00:07:03,530 --> 00:07:04,890
Already did.

104
00:07:05,050 --> 00:07:05,650
The Baicha you know—

105
00:07:05,770 --> 00:07:07,290
no word since he went up there.

106
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:10,570
What are we supposed to do?

107
00:07:16,810 --> 00:07:17,250
[Stop it.]

108
00:07:19,170 --> 00:07:20,610
Hongning!

109
00:07:26,890 --> 00:07:28,130
The Floral Deity

110
00:07:28,330 --> 00:07:28,970
you mentioned

111
00:07:29,210 --> 00:07:30,090
named Jinxiu?

112
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:35,730
Take me where he's been.

113
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:38,570
Who are you?

114
00:07:38,890 --> 00:07:40,370
That's how you ask for help?

115
00:07:40,530 --> 00:07:41,530
Need a lesson?

116
00:07:46,290 --> 00:07:47,730
Sir, this way.

117
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:49,730
Please.

118
00:07:54,290 --> 00:07:54,930
Go ahead.

119
00:07:55,370 --> 00:07:56,250
After you!

120
00:08:18,090 --> 00:08:18,890
Stay right here

121
00:08:19,930 --> 00:08:21,370
and grow nice and quiet.

122
00:08:21,530 --> 00:08:23,170
Don't go bullying my camellias.

123
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:31,410
Help. Help me!

124
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:32,770
Help!

125
00:08:33,610 --> 00:08:34,330
Help!

126
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:46,770
[Help.]

127
00:08:47,930 --> 00:08:48,770
[Help.]

128
00:08:49,570 --> 00:08:50,170
[Help.]

129
00:08:52,210 --> 00:08:53,170
[Help.]

130
00:08:55,210 --> 00:08:55,890
[Help me.]

131
00:09:07,170 --> 00:09:07,890
You alright?

132
00:09:10,730 --> 00:09:12,610
Hi Jinxiu, I'm fine.

133
00:09:13,370 --> 00:09:15,290
What's with the midnight show?

134
00:09:15,690 --> 00:09:16,850
Celestial Floralia's coming.

135
00:09:17,130 --> 00:09:19,090
I have to move the weeds.

136
00:09:19,330 --> 00:09:21,050
So my flower seedlings can take root.

137
00:09:21,530 --> 00:09:22,610
Why not go to

138
00:09:22,930 --> 00:09:23,930
the Flora Grove?

139
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:25,610
Too crowded there.

140
00:09:25,770 --> 00:09:26,930
But they'll thrive here.

141
00:09:28,050 --> 00:09:29,050
Envoy Apricot sent you?

142
00:09:32,210 --> 00:09:33,930
No wonder you got a permit.

143
00:09:35,650 --> 00:09:37,250
It's late. Go home.

144
00:09:37,730 --> 00:09:38,370
I can't.

145
00:09:38,610 --> 00:09:40,410
Must guard my seedlings.

146
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:43,290
The weeds may seem harmless.

147
00:09:43,490 --> 00:09:44,450
But when provoked,

148
00:09:44,610 --> 00:09:46,050
they turn aggressive like that.

149
00:09:46,490 --> 00:09:47,690
At best drain your spiritual energy.

150
00:09:48,010 --> 00:09:49,330
At worst shatter your core.

151
00:09:49,930 --> 00:09:51,610
All more reason to stay.

152
00:09:52,210 --> 00:09:54,210
No flowers,

153
00:09:54,450 --> 00:09:56,010
no access to the Floralia.

154
00:09:56,330 --> 00:09:56,890
Let alone meet

155
00:09:57,050 --> 00:09:58,370
the Floral Deity.

156
00:09:59,210 --> 00:10:00,850
What's the big deal?

157
00:10:01,650 --> 00:10:02,850
It's important.

158
00:10:03,650 --> 00:10:05,050
"She" saved my life.

159
00:10:05,370 --> 00:10:06,890
I must repay

160
00:10:07,330 --> 00:10:08,050
this debt.

161
00:10:09,250 --> 00:10:09,730
Very well.

162
00:10:10,490 --> 00:10:11,330
Listen.

163
00:10:11,810 --> 00:10:12,690
I am the Floral Deity.

164
00:10:13,930 --> 00:10:14,930
Of course you are.

165
00:10:16,210 --> 00:10:16,970
What?

166
00:10:17,650 --> 00:10:19,410
Official Chrysanthemum

167
00:10:19,650 --> 00:10:20,770
claims the title too.

168
00:10:21,010 --> 00:10:22,050
Maybe I was such a deity as well

169
00:10:22,330 --> 00:10:22,930
hundreds of years ago.

170
00:10:23,050 --> 00:10:24,850
Everyone's a deity up here.

171
00:10:25,210 --> 00:10:26,530
But the Floral Deity I seek

172
00:10:26,690 --> 00:10:27,210
has this...

173
00:10:28,530 --> 00:10:29,050
This

174
00:10:29,450 --> 00:10:31,090
mark on "her" forehead.

175
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:32,730
Not someone

176
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:34,010
who just

177
00:10:34,290 --> 00:10:35,810
wanders around like you.

178
00:10:35,930 --> 00:10:36,410
You...

179
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:37,290
Alright, alright.

180
00:10:37,610 --> 00:10:38,890
I know you mean well,

181
00:10:39,290 --> 00:10:40,450
but I have no choice.

182
00:10:40,810 --> 00:10:42,010
Gotta guard my seedlings.

183
00:11:06,050 --> 00:11:07,690
What now, Jinxiu?

184
00:11:08,650 --> 00:11:10,010
Gonna look up some info.

185
00:11:12,490 --> 00:11:12,850
I...

186
00:11:12,970 --> 00:11:13,410
Let's go.

187
00:11:13,810 --> 00:11:14,930
My seedlings.

188
00:11:17,490 --> 00:11:18,210
There's no other way.

189
00:11:19,090 --> 00:11:19,810
Cast a protection charm

190
00:11:19,970 --> 00:11:20,970
around your seedlings.

191
00:11:22,250 --> 00:11:23,330
Don't know how.

192
00:11:24,370 --> 00:11:25,290
Focus your spirit.

193
00:11:25,370 --> 00:11:25,810
Say:

194
00:11:25,970 --> 00:11:27,810
Celestial Guard, by Divine Decree!

195
00:11:28,970 --> 00:11:32,290
Celestial Guard, by Divine Decree!

196
00:11:34,290 --> 00:11:35,410
Why isn't it working?

197
00:11:36,810 --> 00:11:38,250
You haven't had any training.

198
00:11:38,530 --> 00:11:39,530
This incantation's too

199
00:11:39,730 --> 00:11:40,650
advanced for you.

200
00:11:41,610 --> 00:11:42,250
No choice then.

201
00:11:43,010 --> 00:11:44,970
Clear the vines first. Then replant.

202
00:11:45,850 --> 00:11:47,810
Help me, Jinxiu.

203
00:11:48,650 --> 00:11:49,450
Flowers for the Floralia

204
00:11:49,650 --> 00:11:50,570
must be grown by yourself.

205
00:11:50,690 --> 00:11:51,770
Helping you would be cheating.

206
00:11:54,570 --> 00:11:55,090
Well...

207
00:11:56,410 --> 00:11:58,530
Celestial Guard, by Divine Decree!

208
00:12:02,930 --> 00:12:03,730
Won't work.

209
00:12:04,370 --> 00:12:05,170
No one else has

210
00:12:05,530 --> 00:12:07,330
mastered it on the first try except me.

211
00:12:08,090 --> 00:12:08,850
It's working!

212
00:12:09,050 --> 00:12:09,490
Look!

213
00:12:14,210 --> 00:12:15,170
It isn't

214
00:12:15,850 --> 00:12:18,210
as big as mine was.

215
00:12:18,770 --> 00:12:19,250
Big?

216
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:22,890
Celestial Guard, by Divine Decree!

217
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:26,890
Bigger now?

218
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:29,450
[You should thank me for my phalanx.]

219
00:12:29,810 --> 00:12:30,450
Yeah, yeah.

220
00:12:31,610 --> 00:12:32,210
Let's go.

221
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:40,610
You live here?

222
00:12:43,210 --> 00:12:44,810
It looks nice.

223
00:12:47,650 --> 00:12:48,890
But I have a weird feeling…

224
00:12:49,490 --> 00:12:51,130
like I've been here before.

225
00:12:52,450 --> 00:12:53,090
Shh.

226
00:13:15,410 --> 00:13:16,410
The ancient book

227
00:13:16,570 --> 00:13:17,330
only says

228
00:13:17,450 --> 00:13:19,290
vines vanish in a day.

229
00:13:19,570 --> 00:13:20,330
Nothing on

230
00:13:20,490 --> 00:13:21,610
how to cut them early.

231
00:13:28,490 --> 00:13:29,970
What's so funny?

232
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:38,770
I said research the vines,

233
00:13:39,130 --> 00:13:40,330
not read this junk!

234
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:43,290
You put it here. Your stuff.

235
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:44,690
I...

236
00:13:44,810 --> 00:13:47,130
Besides, I can't read anyway.

237
00:13:49,290 --> 00:13:49,770
Fine.

238
00:13:50,490 --> 00:13:51,410
We'll just wait a day

239
00:13:51,530 --> 00:13:52,530
for it to disappear.

240
00:13:55,050 --> 00:13:55,730
Really?

241
00:13:56,210 --> 00:13:56,850
Perfect.

242
00:13:57,170 --> 00:13:58,130
I'm tired anyway.

243
00:13:58,370 --> 00:13:59,130
Time to sleep.

244
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:04,530
Who said you could sleep here?

245
00:14:04,850 --> 00:14:05,450
Get up.

246
00:14:08,330 --> 00:14:09,250
What's wrong?

247
00:14:10,010 --> 00:14:10,970
Am I...

248
00:14:11,210 --> 00:14:12,370
in your way?

249
00:14:12,730 --> 00:14:13,970
I can move over

250
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:14,690
for you to sleep.

251
00:14:17,650 --> 00:14:20,010
A man and woman alone shouldn't

252
00:14:20,530 --> 00:14:21,170
[even share a roof.]

253
00:14:21,730 --> 00:14:22,530
Especially not

254
00:14:22,730 --> 00:14:23,610
sleeping together.

255
00:14:26,890 --> 00:14:28,930
What does that mean?

256
00:14:29,730 --> 00:14:31,010
You and I

257
00:14:31,290 --> 00:14:32,970
can't stay in the same room.

258
00:14:34,570 --> 00:14:36,610
But there's no one else here.

259
00:14:36,810 --> 00:14:38,410
Should we call others in?

260
00:14:39,250 --> 00:14:39,690
You...

261
00:14:40,170 --> 00:14:41,410
This is ridiculous.

262
00:14:44,730 --> 00:14:46,490
It's not appropriate for others

263
00:14:47,170 --> 00:14:47,890
to see us like this.

264
00:14:49,290 --> 00:14:50,690
So many rules.

265
00:14:51,410 --> 00:14:52,730
I'm sleeping anyway.

266
00:14:59,010 --> 00:14:59,530
Get up!

267
00:15:31,850 --> 00:15:34,250
So we can't share a room,

268
00:15:34,530 --> 00:15:35,930
but we can bathe together?

269
00:15:40,450 --> 00:15:41,130
Shut up.

270
00:15:42,130 --> 00:15:42,650
I...

271
00:15:42,770 --> 00:15:43,690
I need peace.

272
00:15:54,250 --> 00:15:55,370
Stay here until

273
00:15:56,090 --> 00:15:57,050
the vines dissolve.

274
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:03,730
Why should we stay here?

275
00:16:04,050 --> 00:16:04,930
To cultivate.

276
00:16:14,530 --> 00:16:15,970
Floralia Palace is lovely.

277
00:16:16,570 --> 00:16:17,490
What's over there?

278
00:16:18,170 --> 00:16:19,210
Quiet.

279
00:16:20,810 --> 00:16:21,090
And there?

280
00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:22,170
Stop talking!

281
00:17:18,369 --> 00:17:18,890
Hey!

282
00:17:20,130 --> 00:17:21,609
Isn't this for bathing?

283
00:17:22,010 --> 00:17:22,770
Get out.

284
00:17:23,609 --> 00:17:25,089
It's fun. Join me?

285
00:17:25,730 --> 00:17:26,290
No.

286
00:17:28,010 --> 00:17:28,410
Come on!

287
00:17:28,569 --> 00:17:28,970
Get in.

288
00:17:29,090 --> 00:17:29,690
Hurry up!

289
00:17:44,770 --> 00:17:45,490
Fun?

290
00:17:45,850 --> 00:17:46,370
Yeah!

291
00:17:54,890 --> 00:17:56,170
I heard something.

292
00:17:56,850 --> 00:17:57,850
You must have misheard.

293
00:17:58,930 --> 00:17:59,770
Check over there.

294
00:17:59,810 --> 00:18:00,330
Okay.

295
00:18:17,410 --> 00:18:18,010
Wake up.

296
00:18:29,930 --> 00:18:30,890
You okay?

297
00:18:31,690 --> 00:18:33,450
Your cheeks are flushed.

298
00:18:34,850 --> 00:18:35,490
It's nothing.

299
00:18:48,010 --> 00:18:48,530
Look.

300
00:18:49,050 --> 00:18:51,170
